'''猴痘'''（{{lang-en|monkeypox}}）是一種由[[病毒|病毒]]引起的[[人畜共通傳染病|人畜共通傳染病]]，即病原體從動物傳播給人類<ref name="WHOnews04June2022">{{cite web |title=Multi-country monkeypox outbreak: situation update |url=https://www.who.int/emergencies/disease-outbreak-news/item/2022-DON390 |accessdate=2022-06-25 |work=www.who.int |publisher=World Health Organization |date=2022-06-04 |language=en |archive-date=2022-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220606225258/https://www.who.int/emergencies/disease-outbreak-news/item/2022-DON390 }}</ref>。感染猴痘的早期症狀包括[[發燒|發燒]]、[[頭痛|頭痛]]、[[肌肉疼痛|肌肉疼痛]]、[[淋巴結腫大|淋巴結腫大]]、[[發冷|發冷]]和[[疲倦|疲倦]]，其後身上出現類似水泡的[[皮疹|皮疹]]並癒合；有些患者會先出現皮疹，或者只出現皮疹<ref name="CDC2017Sym">{{cite web|title=Signs and Symptoms Monkeypox|url=https://www.cdc.gov/poxvirus/monkeypox/symptoms.html|access-date=2017-10-15|date=2015-05-11|publisher=CDC|language=en-us|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015202514/https://www.cdc.gov/poxvirus/monkeypox/symptoms.html|archive-date=2017-10-15|url-status=live}}</ref>。潛伏期通常为7至14天，但也可能为5至21天<ref name="CDC2017Sym"/>；症狀持續時間通常為2至4週<ref name="CDC2017Sym"/>。致死率從0%到11%不等<ref name=WHOfact19May2022/>，絕大多數患者能康復<ref>{{cite web |title=Monkeypox: background information |url=https://www.gov.uk/guidance/monkeypox |accessdate=2022-06-25 |work=GOV.UK |date=2022-06-24 |language=en |archive-date=2022-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220518173849/https://www.gov.uk/guidance/monkeypox }}</ref>。

猴痘由[[猴痘病毒|猴痘病毒]]引起<ref name="CDCabout">{{cite web|title=About Monkeypox|url=https://www.cdc.gov/poxvirus/monkeypox/about.html|accessdate=2022-05-22|date=2021-11-22|website=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention|language=en-us|archive-date=2017-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015202400/https://www.cdc.gov/poxvirus/monkeypox/about.html}}</ref>，該病毒與[[天花病毒|天花病毒]]同屬{{tsl|en|Orthopoxvirus|正痘病毒屬|正痘病毒属}}<ref name="ECDCHP" />。據信，該病毒通常會在[[非洲|非洲]]的某些[[囓齒類|囓齒類]]動物中傳播<ref name="CDCtrans"/>。在可感染人類的兩種猴痘病毒中，[[西非|西非]]類型引發的病症比[[中部非洲|中非]]（剛果盆地）類型的更輕<ref>{{cite journal |title=Clinical features and management of human monkeypox: a retrospective observational study in the UK |journal=The Lancet Infectious Diseases |date=2022-05 |doi=10.1016/S1473-3099(22)00228-6 |pmid=35623380 |accessdate=2022-06-25}}</ref>。患上猴痘的症狀與[[天花|天花]]非常相似，但較爲輕微<ref name=WHOfact19May2022/>。診斷方式為檢測病變部位的病毒[[DNA|DNA]]<ref name="CDC2022Summary">{{cite web |title=Past U.S. Cases and Outbreaks |url=https://www.cdc.gov/poxvirus/monkeypox/outbreak/us-outbreaks.html?CDC_AA_refVal=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fpoxvirus%2Fmonkeypox%2Foutbreak.html |website=www.cdc.gov |accessdate=2022-06-25 |language=en-us |date=2022-06-07 |archive-date=2017-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015202731/https://www.cdc.gov/poxvirus/monkeypox/outbreak.html }}</ref>。

猴痘病毒的人畜傳播途徑包括直接接觸受感染動物的體液或病變部位、食用受感染動物的肉、被動物抓傷或咬傷、接觸受污染的物體等<ref name="Sciencedirect">{{cite web|title=Monkeypox Virus - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/monkeypox-virus|accessdate=2022-05-22|website=Sciencedirect|author1=John E. Bennett MD|archive-date=2022-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610075103/https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/monkeypox-virus}}</ref><ref name="CDCtrans"/>；人與人之間的傳播很少見，主要是透過呼吸道大[[飛沫|飛沫]]傳播，亦可透過[[體液|體液]]傳播<ref name="ECDCHP">{{cite web|title=Factsheet for health professionals on monkeypox|url=https://www.ecdc.europa.eu/en/all-topics-z/monkeypox/factsheet-health-professionals|accessdate=2022-05-22|website=European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control|language=en|archive-date=2022-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220620042406/https://www.ecdc.europa.eu/en/all-topics-z/monkeypox/factsheet-health-professionals}}</ref>。

目前沒有專門針對猴痘的治療方法獲得批准，但一些針對天花的[[抗病毒藥物|抗病毒藥物]]可能對猴痘具有療效<ref name="CDCtreat">{{cite web |date=2021-07-18 |title=Treatment | Monkeypox | Poxvirus | CDC |url=https://www.cdc.gov/poxvirus/monkeypox/clinicians/treatment.html |access-date=2022-05-29 |website=www.cdc.gov |publisher=CDC |language=en-us |archive-date=2019-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190615121759/https://www.cdc.gov/poxvirus/monkeypox/clinicians/treatment.html |url-status=live }}</ref>。此外，[[天花疫苗|天花疫苗]]也可以预防猴痘以及減輕病症，有效率达85%<ref name="CDCtreat"/><ref name=WHOfact19May2022/>。其他預防措施包括勤洗手、避免接觸患病的人或動物<ref name="CDCPre"/>。

1958年，一群從[[新加坡|新加坡]]進口到[[丹麥|丹麥]]一所研究[[脊髓灰質炎|小兒麻痺症]]疫苗的實驗室裡圈養的[[食蟹猴|食蟹猴]]爆發水皰病，是人類首次發現猴痘病毒，因此得名<ref name="ECDCHP" /><ref name="Science20220522">{{cite web|title=Monkeypox outbreak questions intensify as cases soar|url=https://www.science.org/content/article/monkeypox-outbreak-questions-intensify-cases-soar|accessdate=2022-05-22|author=Jon Cohen|date=2022-05-20|website=[[科学_(期刊)|Science]]|language=en|doi=10.1126/science.add1068|archive-date=2022-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220623195404/https://www.science.org/content/article/monkeypox-outbreak-questions-intensify-cases-soar}}</ref>。猴痘病毒的天然[[宿主|宿主]]尚未確定，但最有可能的是[[囓齒目|囓齒類]]動物<ref name=WHOfact19May2022/>。

猴痘的第一例人類病例發生在1970年的[[剛果民主共和國|剛果民主共和國]]<ref name="CDCabout" />，此後非洲平均每年發現幾千例病例，但在非洲以外地區很少發現<ref name="Nature20220520">{{Cite journal |last=Kozlov |first=Max |date=2022-05-20 |title=Monkeypox goes global: why scientists are on alert |url=https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-022-01421-8 |journal=Nature |language=en |doi=10.1038/d41586-022-01421-8 |access-date=2022-05-22 |archive-date=2022-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220524151907/https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-022-01421-8/ }}</ref>。[[2022年猴痘疫情|2022年猴痘疫情]]標誌著非洲以外地區首次發生廣泛的社區傳播，該疫情約2022年5月在[[英國|英國]]開始傳播，隨後在超过40个国家（包括[[歐洲|歐洲]]、[[北美洲|北美洲]]、[[南美洲|南美洲]]、[[亞洲|亞洲]]和[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]）都出現了確診病例<ref>{{cite web|title=Monkeypox cases investigated in Europe, the United States, Canada and Australia|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-61506562|access-date=2022-05-22|website=[[英國廣播公司新聞|BBC News]]|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220519102925/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-61506562}}</ref>。

== 病徵 ==
[[File:Stages_of_monkeypox_lesion_development.jpg|thumb]]
猴痘的{{link-en|前驱症状|Prodrome|早期症状}}包括[[头痛|头痛]]、[[肌肉疼痛|肌肉疼痛]]、[[发热|发热]]和[[疲劳|疲劳]]<ref name=WHOfact19May2022>{{cite web |title=Monkeypox |url=https://www.who.int/news-room/fact-sheets/detail/monkeypox |website=www.who.int |date=2022-05-19 |publisher=World Health Organization |accessdate=2022-05-26 |language=en |archive-date=2022-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220421083742/https://www.who.int/news-room/fact-sheets/detail/monkeypox }}</ref><ref name="Kantele, A. 2016">{{cite journal | vauthors = Kantele A, Chickering K, Vapalahti O, Rimoin AW | title = Emerging diseases-the monkeypox epidemic in the Democratic Republic of the Congo | journal = Clinical Microbiology and Infection | volume = 22 | issue = 8 | pages = 658–659 | date = August 2016 | pmid = 27404372 | doi = 10.1016/j.cmi.2016.07.004 }}</ref>。猴痘的早期病徵可能類似於[[水痘|水痘]]、[[麻疹|麻疹]]和[[天花|天花]]，但[[淋巴結腫大|淋巴結腫大]]是猴痘的特有病徵<ref name=WHOfact19May2022/><ref>{{cite web |author1=Kantele A, Chickering K, Vapalahti O, Rimoin AW (August 2016) |title=Emerging diseases—the monkeypox epidemic in the Democratic Republic of the Congo |url=https://www.clinicalmicrobiologyandinfection.com/article/S1198-743X(16)30228-2/fulltext |website=Clinical Microbiology and Infection |accessdate=2022-06-24}}</ref>。[[皮疹|皮疹]]通常在發熱後1至3天內出現，往往較集中於面部和四肢，而非軀幹上<ref name=WHOfact19May2022/>。[[2022年猴痘爆發|2022年猴痘爆發]]中的許多病例出現了生殖器和肛周病變、發燒、淋巴結腫大和吞嚥疼痛的症狀<ref>{{cite news |title=Multi-country monkeypox outbreak: situation update |url=https://www.who.int/emergencies/disease-outbreak-news/item/2022-DON390 |accessdate=2022-06-24 |work=www.who.int |publisher=World Health Organization |date=2022-06-04 |language=en |archive-date=2022-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220606225258/https://www.who.int/emergencies/disease-outbreak-news/item/2022-DON390 }}</ref>。

皮疹可出現於面部（95%的病例）、手掌和脚掌（75%），也可波及口腔粘膜（70%）、生殖器（30%）、结膜（20%）以及角膜<ref name=WHOfact19May2022/>。[[皮疹|皮疹]]從[[斑疹|斑疹]]（底部平坦的病變）依次演變為[[丘疹|丘疹]]（微凸的堅硬病變）、[[水泡|水泡]]（充滿透明液體的病變）、[[膿疱|膿疱]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cdc.gov.tw/Uploads/1c9605ca-84fb-458d-9c12-6766580f233a.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2022-06-25 |archive-date=2022-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220615063535/https://www.cdc.gov.tw/Uploads/1c9605ca-84fb-458d-9c12-6766580f233a.pdf }}</ref>（充滿淡黃色液體的病變）直到[[結痂|結痂]]並脫落<ref name=WHOfact19May2022/>。病變的數量從幾個到幾千個不等；在嚴重的情況下，病變會合併，直到大部分皮膚脫落<ref name=WHOfact19May2022/>。

病變組織在人體各個部位的發展是同步的<ref name=Goldman2020>{{cite book |last1=Petersen |first1=Brett W. |last2=Damon |first2=Inger K. |editor1-last=Goldman |editor1-first=Lee |editor2-last=Schafer |editor2-first=Andrew I. |title=Goldman-Cecil Medicine |date=2020 |publisher=Elsevier |location=Philadelphia |isbn=978-0-323-53266-2 |pages=2180–2183 |edition=26th |volume=2 |chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=7pKqDwAAQBAJ&dq=monkeypox&pg=PA2180 |chapter=348. Smallpox, monkeypox and other poxvirus infections |access-date=2022-06-24 |archive-date=2022-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220528171332/https://books.google.com/books?id=7pKqDwAAQBAJ&dq=monkeypox&pg=PA2180 }}</ref>，其外觀與天花的皮疹相同<ref name=Kumar2020>{{cite book |last1=Barlow |first1=Gavin |last2=Irving |first2=William L. |last3=Moss |first3=Peter J. |editor1-last=Feather |editor1-first=Adam |editor2-last=Randall |editor2-first=David |editor3-last=Waterhouse |editor3-first=Mona |title=Kumar and Clark's Clinical Medicine |date=2020 |publisher=Elsevier |isbn=978-0-7020-7870-5 |page=517 |edition=10th |chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=sl3sDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA517 |chapter=20. Infectious disease |access-date=2022-05-09 |archive-date=2022-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220505153004/https://books.google.com/books?id=sl3sDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA517 |url-status=live }}</ref>。皮疹通常於十天後結痂並留下疤痕，較嚴重者可能持續2至4周<ref name="CDC2017Sym"/>。病變癒合後可能會留下[[白癜風|白斑]]，然後變成深色疤痕<ref name=Goldman2020/>。

猴痘分两个演化支，分别为刚果盆地（中非）支和西非支，地理分布、严重程度、传染特征区别都很大。前者致死率高达10%，可人传人；后者致死率不足1%，直到[[2022年猴痘爆发|2022年猴痘爆发]]才发现人传人的情况<ref name="Skle">{{Cite journal |last=Sklenovská |first=Nikola |last2=Van Ranst |first2=Marc |date=2018-09-04 |title=Emergence of Monkeypox as the Most Important Orthopoxvirus Infection in Humans |url=https://www.frontiersin.org/article/10.3389/fpubh.2018.00241/full |journal=Frontiers in Public Health |volume=6 |doi=10.3389/fpubh.2018.00241 |issn=2296-2565 |pmc=PMC6131633 |pmid=30234087}}</ref>。

猴痘的潜伏期通常为7至14天，但也可能为5至21天<ref name="CDC2017Sym" />。猴痘的病徵持續14至21天<ref name=WHOfact19May2022/>。

== 傳播 ==
[[File:MonkeyPoxCDC3.png|250px]]
猴痘病毒透過皮膚傷口（即使不可見）、呼吸道或[[粘膜|粘膜]]（眼睛、鼻子或嘴巴）進入人體<ref name="CDCtrans">{{cite web|title=Transmission|url=https://www.cdc.gov/poxvirus/monkeypox/transmission.html|accessdate=2022-05-22|date=2021-07-16|website=CDC|language=en-us|archive-date=2017-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015202658/https://www.cdc.gov/poxvirus/monkeypox/transmission.html}}</ref>。

=== 人畜傳播 ===
非洲有記錄表明，直接接觸受感染動物的血液、體液或皮膚或黏膜損傷，便可能造成動物對人的傳播<ref name=WHOfact19May2022/>；不当食用此类动物也可能是病毒向人类传播的一个重要来源<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Falendysz |first=Elizabeth A. |last2=Lopera |first2=Juan G. |last3=Lorenzsonn |first3=Faye |last4=Salzer |first4=Johanna S. |last5=Hutson |first5=Christina L. |last6=Doty |first6=Jeffrey |last7=Gallardo-Romero |first7=Nadia |last8=Carroll |first8=Darin S. |last9=Osorio |first9=Jorge E. |last10=Rocke |first10=Tonie E. |date=2015-10-30 |editor-last=LaBeaud |editor-first=A. Desiree |title=Further Assessment of Monkeypox Virus Infection in Gambian Pouched Rats (Cricetomys gambianus) Using In Vivo Bioluminescent Imaging |url=https://dx.plos.org/10.1371/journal.pntd.0004130 |journal=PLOS Neglected Tropical Diseases |language=en |volume=9 |issue=10 |doi=10.1371/journal.pntd.0004130 |issn=1935-2735 |pmc=PMC4627722 |pmid=26517839}}</ref>；而居住在森林或附近地區的人亦可能間接或低水平地接觸受感染的動物<ref name=WHOfact19May2022/>。

=== 人際傳播 ===
人與人之間的傳播很少見，但已有交叉感染事件被報導。其主要透過長時間面對面接觸引起的呼吸道大[[飛沫|飛沫]]傳播，也可透過直接接觸感染者的[[體液|體液]]或被污染的物體（如床上用品或衣服）傳播。此外亦有母嬰感染和[[醫療照顧相關感染|醫療照顧相關感染]]的記錄。<ref name="ECDCHP" />

== 病原體 ==
[[File:Monkeypox.gif|缩略图]]
{{Main|猴痘病毒}}
猴痘是由[[猴痘病毒|猴痘病毒]]引起。它是一種有包膜的[[雙鏈DNA病毒|雙鏈DNA病毒]]，屬於[[痘病毒科|痘病毒科]]的{{tsl|en|Orthopoxvirus|正痘病毒屬|正痘病毒属}}（包括[[牛痘病毒|牛痘病毒]]、[[天花病毒|天花病毒]]等痘病毒）<ref name="ECDCHP" />。基因組測序鑑定了兩個系統發育不同的猴痘病毒進化枝——剛果盆地（中非）進化支和西非進化支，前者通常導致更嚴重的疾病、更高的死亡率和更頻繁的人際傳播<ref name="ECDCHP" />。

=== 宿主 ===
猴痘病毒的宿主（主要疾病攜帶者）仍然未知<ref name="CDCabout" />。該病毒於1958年從研究用的[[猴子|猴子]]身上首次被發現，因此該病被命名為「猴痘」<ref name="chp">{{cite web|title=衞生署 衞生防護中心 - 猴痘|url=https://www.chp.gov.hk/tc/healthtopics/content/24/101721.html|accessdate=2022-05-22|website=www.chp.gov.hk|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2022-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220609082043/https://www.chp.gov.hk/tc/healthtopics/content/24/101721.html}}</ref>，不過此名稱屬於用詞不當<ref name="Science20220522" />。據信，非洲[[囓齒目|囓齒類]]動物是猴痘病毒的傳播者<ref name="CDCabout" />。在自然界中已知可攜帶該病毒的物種包括{{link-en|冈比亚袋鼠|Gambian pouched rat}}（''Cricetomys gambianus''）、[[睡鼠科|睡鼠]]、非洲松鼠（[[太陽松鼠|太陽松鼠属]]和[[非洲松鼠屬|非洲松鼠屬]]）等囓齒類動物以及猴子等[[靈長目|靈長類]]動物<ref name="ECDCHP" />。

猴痘病毒的自然史仍存在不確定性，需要進一步研究以確定其確切的宿主以及該病毒如何在自然界中維持循環<ref name=WHOfact19May2022/>。

== 診斷 ==
必須考慮的臨床鑑別診斷包括其他皮疹疾病，如天花（儘管已被消滅）、[[水痘|水痘]]、[[麻疹|麻疹]]、細菌性皮膚感染、[[疥疮|疥瘡]]、[[梅毒|梅毒]]和藥物過敏。在發病初期出現[[淋巴結腫大|淋巴結病]]可能是一個臨床特徵，可用以區別猴痘與天花。猴痘只能由實驗室確診，需要在專業實驗室中通過一些不同的檢測方法測定病毒<ref name=WHOfact19May2022/>。

皮膚損傷樣本的[[聚合酶鏈式反應|聚合酶鏈式反應]]（PCR）測試是首選的實驗室測試。由於病毒不會在血液中停留很長時間，PCR血液檢測通常無法得出結論。如要解釋測試結果，需要發熱日期、皮疹發作日期、樣本採集日期、皮疹當前階段和患者年齡等資訊。<ref name=WHOfact19May2022/>

== 預防 ==
根據[[美国疾病控制与预防中心|美國疾控中心]]（CDC）的建議，一種減毒活病毒疫苗——JYNNEOS（也稱為 Imvamune 或 Imvanex），已被[[美國食品和藥物管理局|美國食品和藥物管理局]]批准用於預防猴痘<ref name="CDCPre">{{cite web|title=Prevention|url=https://www.cdc.gov/poxvirus/monkeypox/prevention.html|accessdate=2022-05-22|date=2019-11-29|website=CDC|language=en-us|archive-date=2022-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220314010736/https://www.cdc.gov/poxvirus/monkeypox/prevention.html}}</ref>。

民眾可以採取多種措施來預防感染猴痘病毒：<ref name="CDCPre" />
*避免接觸可能攜帶病毒的動物（包括在猴痘發生地區生病或被發現死亡的動物）
*避免接觸與生病動物接觸過的任何材料（例如被褥）
*將受感染的患者與可能有感染風險的其他人隔離開來
*與受感染的動物或人類接觸後保持良好的手部衛生（例如用肥皂和水洗手或使用含酒精的洗手液）
*照顧患者時使用[[個人防護裝備|個人防護裝備]] (PPE)

雖然過去已證明，接種[[天花疫苗|天花疫苗]]可預防猴痘，有效率為85%，但在全球消滅天花後，天花疫苗已不再供一般公眾使用。以前接種過天花疫苗可能會減輕猴痘病症<ref name=WHOfact19May2022/>。

[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]指出，提高對風險因素的認識並教育人們可以採取哪些措施來減少接觸病毒是猴痘的主要預防策略<ref name=WHOfact19May2022/>。

== 治療 ==
在[[欧洲联盟|欧盟]]和[[美国|美国]]，{{link-en|替韦立马|Tecovirimat}}被批准用于治疗包括猴痘在内的几种[[痘病毒科|痘病毒]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Tecovirimat SIGA|url=https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/medicines/human/EPAR/tecovirimat-siga|access-date=2022-05-19|date=2022-01-28|publisher=European Medicines Agency|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516151355/https://www.ema.europa.eu/en/medicines/human/EPAR/tecovirimat-siga|archive-date=2022-05-16|url-status=live}}</ref>。

== 流行病學 ==
[[File:Monkeypox_By_Country.svg|thumb]]}}{{leftlegend|#ffc6c6|疑似病例}}]]
=== 非洲首發疫情 ===
首宗人類猴痘病例發現於1970年的[[非洲|非洲]][[剛果民主共和國|剛果民主共和國]]（當時名爲[[薩伊共和國|薩伊共和國]]）赤道地區，患者是一名9歲男童，當時該國已在9個月前根除[[天花|天花]]<ref name="ECDCHP" />。

自1981年至1986年，[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]在剛果民主共和國的監測中記錄了338例人類確診病例和33例死亡病例（致死率約9.8%）<ref name=Skle2>{{cite journal | vauthors = Sklenovská N, Van Ranst M | title = Emergence of Monkeypox as the Most Important Orthopoxvirus Infection in Humans | journal = Frontiers in Public Health | volume = 6 | page = 241 | date = September 2018 | pmid = 30234087 | pmc = 6131633 | doi = 10.3389/fpubh.2018.00241 | doi-access = free }}</ref>。1996至1997年，剛果民主共和國東開賽地區報告了有史以來最大規模的猴痘爆發，經過後續調查共發現了511例人類病例<ref name="ECDCHP" />。剛果盆地疾病分支在剛果民主共和國仍然流行，致死率很高<ref name=Skle2/>。

猴痘病毒的另一個進化支出現在西非，致死率低於1%，但沒有記錄到此進化支的人際傳播，直至[[2022年猴痘爆發|2022年猴痘爆發]]<ref name=Skle/>。

此後，[[中部非洲|中非]]及[[西非|西非]]的[[熱帶雨林|熱帶雨林]]地區出現散發性流行，大型爆發主要集中於剛果民主共和國<ref name="ECDCHP" />。2011年至2014年間，當地每年報告約2000例病例<ref name=Skle/>。現被認爲是[[地方性流行病|風土病]]<ref name="ECDCHP" />。

=== 2003年美國疫情 ===
非洲以外地區首度出現人類病例是在2003年春季時的[[美國|美國]]，感染源是從[[西非|西非]][[加納|加納]]運往美國[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]]的囓齒動物，運抵後與當地的[[土拨鼠|土撥鼠]]同住，人類接觸受感染的土撥鼠後染病<ref name="ECDCHP" />。此次疫情導致美國出現70多例猴痘病例<ref name=WHOfact19May2022/>。

=== 2017–2019年尼日利亞疫情 ===
2017年9月，[[尼日利亚|尼日利亚]]爆发了当地40年以来规模最大的猴痘疫情，有311例疑似病例和132例確診病例<ref name="ECDCHP" /><ref name=WHOfact19May2022/>。

=== 2018年英国病例 ===
2018年9月，[[英国|英国]]出现了首例猴痘病例。此人是一名尼日利亚国民，据信在前往英国之前在尼日利亚感染了猴痘<ref>{{cite news|title=First ever case of monkeypox recorded in the UK|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2018/sep/08/first-ever-case-of-monkeypox-recorded-in-the-uk|access-date=2018-09-08|work=The Guardian|date=2018-09-08|language=en|archive-date=2018-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180908204740/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2018/sep/08/first-ever-case-of-monkeypox-recorded-in-the-uk|url-status=live}}</ref>。{{link-en|英格兰公共卫生局|Public Health England}}称，此人在被转移到{{link-en|皇家自由医院|皇家自由医院}}的专门传染病科之前，曾住在[[康沃尔|康沃尔]]的一个海军基地。英格兰公共卫生局在跟踪与患者有过密切接触的人，以提供建议并在必要时对其进行监测<ref>{{cite news|title=Monkeypox case in England|url=https://www.gov.uk/government/news/monkeypox-case-in-england|access-date=2018-09-08|work=[[gov.uk|gov.uk]]|date=2018-09-08|language=en|archive-date=2018-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180908192919/https://www.gov.uk/government/news/monkeypox-case-in-england|url-status=live}}</ref>。2018年9月11日，[[黑池镇|黑池镇]]确诊了第二例病例<ref>{{cite web|title=Blackpool monkeypox case confirmed as second in UK|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-lancashire-45490444|access-date=2018-09-11|date=2018-09-11|publisher=BBC News|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180911184326/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-lancashire-45490444|archive-date=2018-09-11|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |last=Vaughan |first=Aisling |last2=Aarons |first2=Emma |last3=Astbury |first3=John |last4=Balasegaram |first4=Sooria |last5=Beadsworth |first5=Mike |last6=Beck |first6=Charles R |last7=Chand |first7=Meera |last8=O’Connor |first8=Catherine |last9=Dunning |first9=Jake |last10=Ghebrehewet |first10=Sam |last11=Harper |first11=Nick |date=2018-09-20 |title=Two cases of monkeypox imported to the United Kingdom, September 2018 |url=https://www.eurosurveillance.org/content/10.2807/1560-7917.ES.2018.23.38.1800509 |journal=Eurosurveillance |language=en |volume=23 |issue=38 |doi=10.2807/1560-7917.ES.2018.23.38.1800509 |issn=1560-7917 |pmc=PMC6157091 |pmid=30255836 |access-date=2022-05-23 |archive-date=2022-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220622051635/https://www.eurosurveillance.org/content/10.2807/1560-7917.ES.2018.23.38.1800509 }}</ref>，同月26日确诊第三例，是照顾黑池镇病例的一名医务工作者<ref>{{cite web|title=Medic becomes third person infected with monkeypox in England|url=https://www.theguardian.com/society/2018/sep/26/medic-becomes-third-person-infected-with-monkeypox-in-england|access-date=2018-09-26|date=2018-09-26|last=Gayle|first=Damien|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180926170017/https://www.theguardian.com/society/2018/sep/26/medic-becomes-third-person-infected-with-monkeypox-in-england|archive-date=2018-09-26|name-list-style=vanc|url-status=live}}</ref>。第四起病例于2019年12月3日出现在[[西南英格兰|西南英格兰]]，患者从尼日利亚前往英国<ref name="PHE4Dec2019">{{cite web|title=Monkeypox case confirmed in England|url=https://www.gov.uk/government/news/monkeypox-case-confirmed-in-england|access-date=2019-12-12|date=2019-12-04|website=GOV.UK|publisher=[[Public_Health_England|Public Health England]]|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212092044/https://www.gov.uk/government/news/monkeypox-case-confirmed-in-england|archive-date=2019-12-12|url-status=live}}</ref>。

=== 2019年新加坡病例 ===
2019年5月8日，一名来自尼日利亚的38岁男子被确认为该国首例猴痘患者后，在[[新加坡国家传染病中心|新加坡国家传染病中心]]的隔离病房住院治疗。共有22人被隔离<ref name="CIDRAPMay2019">{{cite web|title=News Scan for May 09, 2019, Singapore sees first monkeypox case – in Nigerian national|url=http://www.cidrap.umn.edu/news-perspective/2019/05/news-scan-may-09-2019|access-date=2019-05-10|website=CIDRAP|publisher=Center for Infectious Disease Research and Policy, [[明尼苏达大学|University of Minnesota]]|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190510020038/http://www.cidrap.umn.edu/news-perspective/2019/05/news-scan-may-09-2019|archive-date=2019-05-10|url-status=live}}</ref>。该病例可能与尼日利亚正在爆发的疫情有关<ref name="WHO_May_2019">{{cite web|title=Monkeypox – Singapore|url=https://www.who.int/emergencies/disease-outbreak-news/item/16-may-2019-monkeypox-singapore-en|access-date=2022-05-23|date=2019-05-16|publisher=[[World_Health_Organization|World Health Organization]]|archive-date=2022-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220621041736/https://www.who.int/emergencies/disease-outbreak-news/item/16-may-2019-monkeypox-singapore-en}}</ref>。

=== 2022年全球疫情 ===
{{main|2022年猴痘爆发}}

2022年5月，[[英國|英國]]發現多個病例，證實猴痘病毒持續爆發<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.theatlantic.com/health/archive/2022/05/monkeypox-outbreak-covid-pandemic/629920/ | title=So, Have You Heard About Monkeypox? | website=[[The_Atlantic|The Atlantic]] | date=19 May 2022 | access-date=2022-06-24 | archive-date=2022-06-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220623122621/https://www.theatlantic.com/health/archive/2022/05/monkeypox-outbreak-covid-pandemic/629920/ }}</ref>。5月6日首例確診，該人士曾到訪[[尼日利亞|尼日利亞]]（猴痘流行地區）<ref name="WHO12">{{cite web |date=16 May 2022 |title=Monkeypox – United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland |url=https://www.who.int/emergencies/disease-outbreak-news/item/2022-DON381 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220517223855/https://www.who.int/emergencies/disease-outbreak-news/item/2022-DON381 |archive-date=17 May 2022 |access-date=17 May 2022 |publisher=World Health Organization}}</ref>。從5月18日起，越來越多的國家和地區報告了病例，主要是在歐洲，亦出現於[[北美洲|北美洲]]和[[南美洲|南美洲]]、[[亞洲|亞洲]]、[[非洲|非洲]]和[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]{{refn|<ref name="arg">{{cite web|date=26 May 2022|title=Viruela del mono: confirmaron el primer caso del virus en el país|url=https://www.lanacion.com.ar/sociedad/viruela-del-mono-confirmaron-el-primer-caso-del-virus-en-el-pais-nid26052022/|access-date=26 May 2022|language=es|archive-date=2022-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220624004100/https://www.lanacion.com.ar/sociedad/viruela-del-mono-confirmaron-el-primer-caso-del-virus-en-el-pais-nid26052022/}}</ref><ref name="alarabiya">{{cite web |title=UAE reports first case of monkeypox in the country |url=https://english.alarabiya.net/News/gulf/2022/05/24/UAE-reports-first-case-of-monkeypox-in-the-country |website=[[Al_Arabiya|Al Arabiya]] |date=24 May 2022 |access-date=24 May 2022 |archive-date=24 May 2022 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220524192332/https://english.alarabiya.net/News/gulf/2022/05/24/UAE-reports-first-case-of-monkeypox-in-the-country |url-status=live }}</ref><ref name="1stisrael">{{Cite news|first=Ido|last=Efrati|title=Israel Confirms First Case of Monkeypox Virus|language=en|work=Haaretz|url=https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/israel-discovers-first-case-of-monkeypox-virus-1.10812439|access-date=21 May 2022|archive-date=20 May 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220520192033/https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/israel-discovers-first-case-of-monkeypox-virus-1.10812439|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="aus">{{cite web |date=20 May 2022 |title=Monkeypox confirmed in Melbourne and Sydney |url=https://www.abc.net.au/news/2022-05-20/monkeypox-case-in-sydney-and-melbourne/101084864 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220520071749/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2022-05-20/monkeypox-case-in-sydney-and-melbourne/101084864 |archive-date=20 May 2022 |access-date=20 May 2022 |publisher=[[Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation|Australian Broadcasting Corporation]]}}</ref><ref name="moroc1st">{{cite web |title=Morocco Reports First Monkeypox Case |url=https://www.moroccoworldnews.com/2022/06/349441/morocco-reports-first-monkeypox-case |website=[[Morocco_World_News|Morocco World News]] |access-date=2 June 2022 |archive-date=2022-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220621015327/https://www.moroccoworldnews.com/2022/06/349441/morocco-reports-first-monkeypox-case }}</ref><ref name="ghanafirstcase">{{cite web |title=5 cases of monkeypox confirmed in Ghana |url=https://www.myjoyonline.com/5-cases-of-monkeypox-confirmed-in-ghana/ |website=MyJoyOnline.com |access-date=8 June 2022 |archive-date=2022-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220621191942/https://www.myjoyonline.com/5-cases-of-monkeypox-confirmed-in-ghana/ }}</ref>}} 。截至6月24日，已確診4,126例病例<ref name="OurWorldinData1">{{cite web |title=Monkeypox Data Explorer |url=https://ourworldindata.org/explorers/monkeypox?tab=table&time=2022-05-24..latest&facet=none&Metric=Confirmed+cases&Frequency=Cumulative&Shown+by=Date+of+confirmation&country=~OWID_WRL |access-date=27 May 2022 |website=OurWorldInData}}</ref>。

